      #sideScrollerMenu
        p.hot_links_header Hot Links
        ul.sideScrollerMenuItems
          li
            a(href='#valley_experience') Valley Experience
          li
            a(href='#curriculum') Curriculum
          li
            a(href='#portfolio') Program Dates
          li
            a(href='#mentors') Mentors
          li
            a(href='#placement') Placement Assurance
          li
            a(href='#tution') Tuition & Financing
          li
            a(href='#money') Money back guarantee

    #menu2.col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12.visible-sm.visible-xs(style='float: left;')
      #sideScrollerMenu2
        p.hot_links_header Hot Links
        ul.sideScrollerMenuItems
          li
            a(href='#valley_experience') Valley Experience
          li
            a(href='#curriculum') Curriculum
          li
            a(href='#portfolio') Program Dates
          li
            a(href='#mentors') Mentors
          li
            a(href='#placement') Placement Assurance
          li
            a(href='#tution') Tuition & Financing
          li
            a(href='#money') Money back guarantee
          li
            a(href='#faq') FAQ

    .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-9.col-lg-9(style='float: right;')
      .clearfix

      section
        .row
          .col-md-12.text-center
            .section-header
              h2 Valley Experience
              p
                | Valley experience is all about learning to code in an effective and proper way. It helps build your fundamentals
                | strong in technology. Valley experience coupled with intensive coding bootcamp will not only make an individual
                | learn to code but it also helps the individual launch his career. We here at valley are committed in providing
                | quality knowledge through our cutting edge training methodologies. We are the first coding bootcamp in
                | bangalore who are working together to make developers better every day.
        .row.text-center
          .col-lg-3.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-12.mb-lg-0.mb-4
            .services-item.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='0.4s')
              .service-icon
                img(src='/assets/img/homepage/service/serviceicon03.png', alt='Service Icon 1')
              h4 Pre work
              p
                | Before you get started with learning from valley, start your pre work. You will be given a certain amount
                | of study material to finish before you start learning in valley.
          .col-lg-3.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-12.mb-lg-0.mb-4
            .services-item.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='0.3s')
              .service-icon
                i.icofont.icofont-earphone
              h4 Learn at valley
              p
                | At valley, you will undergo a stringent hands on coding exercise in the supervision of some renowned instructors.
                | Get ready to put your coding hat on.
          .col-lg-3.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-12.mb-lg-0.mb-md-0.mb-4
            .services-item.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='0.2s')
              .service-icon
                img(src='/assets/img/homepage/service/serviceicon02.png', alt='Service Icon 2')
              h4 Placement training
              p
                | The moment you finish learning in the bootcamp, we directly start you placement training. This is again instructor
                | led. We know what is usually asked in the interviews, and we prepare you exactly for that.
          .col-lg-3.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-12
            .services-item.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='0.1s')
              .service-icon
                i.icofont.icofont-social-concrete5
              h4 Post valley bootcamp
              p
                | We provide students support once they get placed too. You will have access to our instructors, study materials
                | etc even after you graduate.

      section#curriculum.section-padding
        .row
          .col-md-12.text-center
            .section-header
              h2 Curriculum
              p
                | This course will start with an introduction to python programming. The course covers all the topics needed
                | to be a good backend developer. On the scripting part, we cover Linux and shell scripting. We also go through
                | the basics of github. We start with setting up the environment using python, pip and pycharm. We go through
                | how a rest api works and also implement few of them. Our database lessons will include, mongoDb and SQL
                | and we also teach some basics in cloud computing like EC2, dynamoDb, RDS, S3 etc.
              br
              p
                | This course will introduce the learner to applied machine learning, focusing more on the techniques and methods
                | than on the statistics behind these methods. The course will start with a discussion of how machine learning
                | is different than descriptive statistics. The issue of dimensionality of data will be discussed, and the
                | task of clustering data, as well as evaluating those clusters, will be tackled. Supervised approaches for
                | creating predictive models will be described. The course will end with a look at more advanced techniques,
                | such as building ensembles, and practical limitations of predictive models. By the end of this course,
                | students will be able to identify the difference between a supervised (classification) and unsupervised
                | (clustering) technique, identify which technique they need to apply for a particular dataset and need,
                | engineer features to meet that need, and write python code to carry out an analysis
              .row
                .col-xs-6.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-3
                  .courseWrapper
                    center
                      p
                        b Week 1
                      p Introduction to Python + ML
                .col-xs-6.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-3
                  .courseWrapper
                    center
                      p
                        b Week 2
                      p Linux And Shell Scripting.
                .col-xs-6.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-3
                  .courseWrapper
                    center
                      p
                        b Week 3
                      p Python, PIP, Pycharm.
                .col-xs-6.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-3
                  .courseWrapper
                    center
                      p
                        b Week 4
                      p Understanding REST API.
                .col-xs-6.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-3
                  .courseWrapper
                    center
                      p
                        b Week 5
                      p Build your own rest api.
                .col-xs-6.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-3
                  .courseWrapper
                    center
                      p
                        b Week 6
                      p Databases: MongoDb, SQL
                .col-xs-6.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-3
                  .courseWrapper
                    center
                      p
                        b Week 7
                      p Cloud Computing: EC2, S3 etc.
                .col-xs-6.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-3
                  .courseWrapper
                    center
                      p
                        b Week 8
                      p Interview preparation. DS and Algos.
                .col-xs-6.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-3
                  .courseWrapper
                    center
                      p
                        b Week 9
                      p
                        | Introduction to Machine Learning, Probability, Conditional Probability, Bayes Theorem.
                .col-xs-6.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-3
                  .courseWrapper
                    center
                      p
                        b Week 10
                      p Statistics, Linear Regression, Logistics Regression.
                .col-xs-6.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-3
                  .courseWrapper
                    center
                      p
                        b Week 11
                      p Supervised/Unsupervised learning, Distance measures, Artificial neural networks.
                .col-xs-6.col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-3
                  .courseWrapper
                    center
                      p
                        b Week 12
                      p Clustering and Classification.
              br
              br
              a.boxed-btn(href='docs/The Valley Bootcamp - Python Machine Learning.pdf', target='_blank')
                | Download Syllabus
                i#portfolio.icofont.icofont-long-arrow-right

      section
        .row
          .col-md-6.offset-md-3.text-center
            .section-header
              h2 Program Dates
        .row
          .col-lg-12.col-md-12.col-sm-12.mb-lg-0.mb-4(style='margin-top:-70px;')
            .pricing-tale.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='0.1s')
              .prcing-head
                center
                  h3 Python + Machine Learning
              br
              .features
                ul(style='text-align: center;')
                  li Start date - 20 May 2018
                  li Location - Bangalore

      section#mentors.section-padding
        .row
          .col-md-6.offset-md-3.text-center
            .section-header
              h2 Mentors
              p.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='0.1s')
                | Top notch software engineers with a combined experience of more than 15 years of software development experience.
        .row
          .col-md-12
            .testimonial-carousel.text-center
              .single-testimonial
                .img-rounded
                  img(src='/images/new/sunil_small.jpg', alt='Sunil')
                h4 Sunil
