                  br
                  |  Boston
                p
                  a(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/nandeesh-hasbi-34157b45/')
                    i.fa.fa-linkedin(aria-hidden='true')
              .single-testimonial
                .img-rounded
                  img(src='/images/new/teamx.jpg', alt='We are hiring')
                h4 We are hiring
                p.title
                  | Mentors
                  br
                  |  Bangalore
                p
                p
                  a(href='mailto:thevalleybootcamp@gmail.com') Apply

      section#placement.section-padding-top
        .row
          .col-md-6.offset-md-3.text-center
            .section-header
              h2 Placement assurance
              p You graduate from Valley and you will get jobs. Period.
        .row.text-center
          .col-lg-3.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-12.mb-lg-0.mb-4
            .features-item.item-1.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='0.1s')
              i.icofont.icofont-earphone
              h5 Money back guarantee
              p.small
                | If you don't get a job within 6 months of graduation, we will refund you your tuition.
          .col-lg-3.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-12.mb-lg-0.mb-4
            .features-item.item-2.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='0.2s')
              i.icofont.icofont-vehicle-crane
              h5 Online presence
              p.small
                | Once you graduate, you will have strong and unique portfolio presence in github. You will be doing close
                | to 3 projects during the class hours. We help you increase your marketability along with helping you to
                | learn to code.
          .col-lg-3.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-12.mb-md-0.mb-lg-0.mb-4
            .features-item.item-3.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='0.3s')
              i.icofont.icofont-architecture-alt
              h5 Excellent placement team
              p.small
                | We have a top notch placement team which is constantly looking to place our candidates into various companies.
                | Our proven track record in placement is an example on how good our placement team is.
          .col-lg-3.col-md-6.col-sm-6.col-12
            .features-item.item-4.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='0.4s')
              i.icofont.icofont-brand-tribenet
              h5 Practise, practise, practise
              p.small
                | And at last, you will undergo rigorous practise sessions in the form of mock interviews, whiteboard coding
                | challenges, group discussions etc.

      section#tution.section-padding-top
        .row
          .col-md-6.offset-md-3.text-center
            .section-header
              h2 Tuition & Financing
              p Affordable and pocket friendly pricing
        .row
          .col-lg-12.col-md-12.col-sm-12.mb-lg-0.mb-4
            .pricing-tale.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='0.1s')
              .prcing-head
                center
                  h3 Python and Machine Learning along with Placements
              br
              br
              .features
                ul(style='text-align: center;')
                  li
                    i.icofont.icofont-tick-mark
                    |  Pay full : INR 29,999 + GST
                  li
                    i.icofont.icofont-tick-mark
                    |  Study now, pay later with
